  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Real-Time Strategy Defense]</h2>Skel dungeon is a real-time strategy defense game.<br>Control the Skel to set up traps and defeat the heroes yourself.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Setting Trap]</h2>At night, you can manage the dungeon.<br>Place traps where heroes are likely to invade to prepare for their assault.<br>Set up and upgrade trap rooms and expand your dungeon.<br>Discover various artifacts and find hidden combination rooms with new effects.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/32997de0307cbd16ce910ac262b61f2d.poster.avif?t=1729547709\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/32997de0307cbd16ce910ac262b61f2d.webm?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/32997de0307cbd16ce910ac262b61f2d.mp4?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Skel's Transformation & Combat]</h2>During the day, you must control the Skel to directly engage in combat against incoming heroes.<br>Steal heroes' heads and use their abilities.<br>Use various transformations such as swords, magic, shields, and throwing stars to effectively defeat heroes according to the situation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/54a9ae536b61c6465fdd6526aafd2d36.poster.avif?t=1729547709\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/54a9ae536b61c6465fdd6526aafd2d36.webm?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/54a9ae536b61c6465fdd6526aafd2d36.mp4?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Stages & Endless Mode]</h2>Face increasingly powerful heroes and clear all seven stages.<br>Achieve high scores through the endless mode with random waves and effects.<br>After completing stages and endless mode, earn higher scores to compete for rankings with other players.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/2e215a3b5956bac407065e53294eeb0c.poster.avif?t=1729547709\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/2e215a3b5956bac407065e53294eeb0c.webm?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/2e215a3b5956bac407065e53294eeb0c.mp4?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Repeat play]</h2>You can't resurrect the Demon Lord all at once, sacrifice heroes repeatedly.<br>Use the characteristic points obtained after completing stages to enhance traps and Skel, and create your own build.<br>Unlock new trap rooms, transformations, and skins, and play with them.<br>Adjust the difficulty as you like through perks and modifications, and earn bonus points.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/cc0360e65ce90fae679d9ac69191fe6d.poster.avif?t=1729547709\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/cc0360e65ce90fae679d9ac69191fe6d.webm?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/cc0360e65ce90fae679d9ac69191fe6d.mp4?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Real-Time Strategy Defense]</h2>Skel dungeon is a real-time strategy defense game.<br>Control the Skel to set up traps and defeat the heroes yourself.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Setting Trap]</h2>At night, you can manage the dungeon.<br>Place traps where heroes are likely to invade to prepare for their assault.<br>Set up and upgrade trap rooms and expand your dungeon.<br>Discover various artifacts and find hidden combination rooms with new effects.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/32997de0307cbd16ce910ac262b61f2d.poster.avif?t=1729547709\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/32997de0307cbd16ce910ac262b61f2d.webm?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/32997de0307cbd16ce910ac262b61f2d.mp4?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Skel's Transformation & Combat]</h2>During the day, you must control the Skel to directly engage in combat against incoming heroes.<br>Steal heroes' heads and use their abilities.<br>Use various transformations such as swords, magic, shields, and throwing stars to effectively defeat heroes according to the situation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/54a9ae536b61c6465fdd6526aafd2d36.poster.avif?t=1729547709\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/54a9ae536b61c6465fdd6526aafd2d36.webm?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/54a9ae536b61c6465fdd6526aafd2d36.mp4?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Stages & Endless Mode]</h2>Face increasingly powerful heroes and clear all seven stages.<br>Achieve high scores through the endless mode with random waves and effects.<br>After completing stages and endless mode, earn higher scores to compete for rankings with other players.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/2e215a3b5956bac407065e53294eeb0c.poster.avif?t=1729547709\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/2e215a3b5956bac407065e53294eeb0c.webm?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/2e215a3b5956bac407065e53294eeb0c.mp4?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Repeat play]</h2>You can't resurrect the Demon Lord all at once, sacrifice heroes repeatedly.<br>Use the characteristic points obtained after completing stages to enhance traps and Skel, and create your own build.<br>Unlock new trap rooms, transformations, and skins, and play with them.<br>Adjust the difficulty as you like through perks and modifications, and earn bonus points.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/cc0360e65ce90fae679d9ac69191fe6d.poster.avif?t=1729547709\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/cc0360e65ce90fae679d9ac69191fe6d.webm?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2963830/extras/cc0360e65ce90fae679d9ac69191fe6d.mp4?t=1729547709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
